@database RtgCheckVSync
@node main "RtgCheckVSync"
@toc main

   NAME
        RtgCheckVSync - Check, if the ray is currently inside Vertical Blank Gap

   SYNOPSIS
        RtgCheckVSync(RtgScreen)
                       A0

        int RtgCheckVSync(struct RtgScreen *)

   FUNCTION
        This function returns 0, if the ray is OUTSIDE the Vertical Blank Gap, 1, if
        it is INSIDE, and 2, if this is not supported by the GFX Board (in which
        case a RtgWaitTOF() will be done by this function).

   INPUTS
        RtgScreen - The RtgScreen of the GFX Board to be used

   SEE ALSO
        @{" RtgWaitTOF " link "rtgmaster/RtgWaitTOF/Main"}

@endnode
                                 
